Pentaho Report Test Framework

prereqs for running:
  * Maven
  * PDI 4.1.0 w/Reporting Output Step installed
  * set up PDI db connection params

prereqs for dev only:
  * Eclipse (Helios) with Groovy plugin

conventions:
  * dir structure of presto files matches dir(s) w/reports

